  "notes": [
    "Edit spawnGroups.regular.spawnWeights to tune non-Orbital Satellite threats.",
    "Weights are relative values: 0 disables a regular threat, larger numbers make it more likely.",
    "miniBoss is special: a value above 0 schedules one mini boss 10 seconds after entering that wave, instead of adding it to random spawn rolls.",
    "Edit spawnGroups.regular.spawnInterval to tune the cooldown for non-Orbital Satellite threats.",
    "Edit spawnGroups.orbitalSatellite.enabled and spawnGroups.orbitalSatellite.spawnInterval to tune Orbital Satellite independently.",
    "Edit threatParams to tune score, radius, inbound speed, entry angle randomness, and per-wave growth.",
    "Each numeric range uses base + currentWave * wave + random(0, random), then wave modifiers are applied.",
    "spawnAngle.spreadDegrees controls where objects enter from. 360 means all around the screen.",
    "aimRadius controls inbound angle randomness: larger values let objects aim farther away from the planet center.",
    "When the game reaches a wave beyond this list, it loops these entries from the beginning."
